trans-unit.source: Represents the <see langword="<EncryptionProperty>" /> element used in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Representa o elemento <see langword="<EncryptionProperty>" /> usado na criptografia XML.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionProperty> class encapsulates the `<EncryptionProperty>` element defined by the World Wide Web Consortium XML Encryption specification located at http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionProperty> classe encapsula o `<EncryptionProperty>` elemento definido pela especificação de criptografia de XML do World Wide Web Consortium localizado em http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionProperty> class to provide additional encryption information related to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionProperty> classe para fornecer informações adicionais de criptografia relacionadas a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> e <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elementos.

trans-unit.source: For example, use this class to specify a time stamp.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, use essa classe para especificar um carimbo de hora.
